remarks: The ordering of the field of complex numbers.  (Note that this is not actually an ordering on ` CC ` , but we put it in the structure anyway because restricting to ` RR ` does not affect this component, so that ` ( CCfld |``s RR ) ` is an ordered field even though ` CCfld ` itself is not.)
